4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aspiring to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly with a class size limit of 16 participants. It covers vital areas such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Participants will learn to manage risks with data loss prevention strategies and navigate compliance with international standards, including ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates will receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop